1. Making forms responsive

class = "table-responsive"

e.g.

<div class="col-xs-3 table-responsive">
              <input type="text" class="form-control " placeholder="Enter Project Name">
              <br>
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-block btn-success .btn-sm " onclick="location.href = 'boards_test1.html';">Create Project</button>
            </div>  



2. Button + Javascript + href


<button type="button" onclick="location.href = '[my_page].html';"  >
[Name_of_button]</button>
            
e.g. 

<button type="button" class="btn btn-block btn-success .btn-sm " onclick="location.href = 'boards_test1.html';">Create Project</button>





